summary: The best Fake love Look so far...
title: The best Fake love Look so far...
body:
LOVE those outfits, why didn’t they wear that at the BBMAS? They look like Princes of a faraway galaxy. It’s “manga” but not too much. Does it make any sense? Do I make any sense?

After walking around many times wearing just one sleeve of his jacket, Jimin has finally decided to just CUT one. Well done!

I really love this part of the choreography.

I don’t know about you, but even if I really like Jimin’s split, I don’t trust it. I don’t trust it in the long term, with a world tour and rehearsals etc. Can he do something less challenging? Like….just standing….I know I shoudln’t worry….
